                <p rend="center">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Control and Administration of Germany</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Council discussed the issues raised in the memorandum of the French
                    Delegation (C.F.M.(45) 17)<note n="42" xml:id="d150fn42">September 13, <ref target="#pg_177">p. 177</ref>.</note> on the control and administration
                    of Germany.</p>
                <pb facs="0412" n="400" xml:id="pg_400"/>
                <p>No decisions were reached and the Council agreed to resume their discussion of
                    these issues at their next meeting.</p>
            </div>
